  "keyFeatures": [
    "Modern post-exploitation C2 framework with multiplayer support",
    "Demon agent with sleep obfuscation (Ekko, FOLIAGE) and indirect syscalls",
    "Cross-platform Qt-based client with dark UI",
    "Customizable C2 profiles using YAOTL format",
    "HTTP/HTTPS and SMB listeners",
    "Token vault for credential management",
    "COFF loader and Beacon API compatibility",
    "External C2 and custom agent support",
    "Python API for extensibility",
    "Module system for adding functionality"
  ],
